# MongoDB

## Introduction

### Start Mongo Server

    mongod --dbpath ./mongo-db/

### Start Mongo CLI

    mongosh mongodb://127.0.0.1:27017

## Create Database

    use imdb

## Create Collections (Tables)

    db.createCollection("movies")
    db.createCollection("episodes")
    db.createCollection("persons")
    db.createCollection("characters")
    db.createCollection("directors")
    db.createCollection("genres")
    db.createCollection("knownformovies")
    db.createCollection("principals")
    db.createCollection("professions")
    db.createCollection("ratings")
    db.createCollection("titles")
    db.createCollection("writers")
    
    show collections

## ReplicaSet

    mongod –port 27017 –dbpath ./mongod/db1 –replSet rs0
    mongod –port 27018 –dbpath ./mongod/db2 –replSet rs0

    mongosh –port 27017
    rs.initiate()
    rs.status()
    rs.add("localhost:27018")
    
    mongosh –port 27018
    rs.status()
    rs.secondaryOk()